OL,3,CBargain-hunting shoppers give
OL,4,Cretailers welcome January boost
OL,6,FBargain-hunting shoppers gave
OL,7,Fretailers a welcome boost in January
OL,8,Ffollowing a disappointing festive
OL,9,Fperiod, figures show.
OL,11,FTotal UK footfall increased by 6.6%
OL,12,Fyear on year in January, a significant
OL,13,Fjump from December when retailers saw
OL,14,F2.2% fewer shoppers than the previous
OL,15,FChristmas, according to British Retail
OL,16,FConsortium (BRC)-Sensormatic data.
OL,18,FHigh street footfall increased by
OL,19,F4.5%, while visits to retail parks and
OL,20,Fshopping centres were up 7.9% and 7.4%
OL,21,Frespectively.
