OL,3,CBargain-hunting shoppers give
OL,4,Cretailers welcome January boost
OL,6,FFootfall was up year on year in all
OL,7,Ffour UK nations, with Wales improving
OL,8,Fby 8.5%, England by 7.4%, Northern
OL,9,FIreland by 3.5% and Scotland seeing a
OL,10,F1% improvement.
OL,12,FStore visits increased substantially
OL,13,Fin the first week of the month as many
OL,14,Fconsumers hit the January sales in
OL,15,Ftheir local area, with shopping
OL,16,Fcentres faring particularly well.
OL,18,FFootfall remained positive across
OL,19,Fmajor UK cities over the month despite
OL,20,Fsnowy weather and Storm Eowyn causing
OL,21,Fdisruption in some areas.
