OL,3,CBargain-hunting shoppers give
OL,4,Cretailers welcome January boost
OL,6,FBRC chief executive Helen Dickinson
OL,7,Fsaid: "Improved shopper traffic is
OL,8,Fwelcome news for high streets
OL,9,Ffollowing a particularly difficult
OL,10,Fgolden quarter to end 2024, and low
OL,11,Fconsumer sentiment to start the year.
OL,13,F"Retailers want to invest more in
OL,14,Fstores and staff to enhance the
OL,15,Fshopping experience for customers and
OL,16,Fhelp to grow the economy, but the
OL,17,Fswathe of additional costs from April
OL,18,Fwill limit investment and lead to job
OL,19,Flosses and higher prices at the tills."
