OL,3,CBargain-hunting shoppers give
OL,4,Cretailers welcome January boost
OL,6,FAndy Sumpter, from Sensormatic, said:
OL,7,F"After a dreary December, retailers
OL,8,Fwill welcome January's footfall jump.
OL,10,F"While welcome, after months of
OL,11,Ferratic and constrained footfall, the
OL,12,Fjury's out as to whether January's
OL,13,Fstore performance signals the start of
OL,14,Fa sustained high street revival or if
OL,15,Fit will be a flash in the pan come
OL,16,FFebruary.
