OL,3,CBargain-hunting shoppers give
OL,4,Cretailers welcome January boost
OL,6,F"And, even if shopper traffic recovery
OL,7,Fhas finally turned a corner, the
OL,8,Fchallenge for retailers will be
OL,9,Fsolving the next conundrum; how they
OL,10,Fbalance enhanced footfall ` which
OL,11,Frequires optimised store staffing to
OL,12,Fconvert into sales ` and the
OL,13,Fsignificant rises to labour costs
OL,14,Fborne out of the Budget on the one
OL,15,Fhand, with consumer appetite for
OL,16,Fdiscounts ` a long-term margin-eroder
OL,17,F` on the other, which will not be an
OL,18,Feasy circle to square."
